#108MPCaptureInfinity

On March 15,2021 Realme announced a blind sale of their latest smartphone Realme 8 Pro.
The phone is equipped with an 108MP camera based on Samsung ISOCELL HM2 Sensor having 1/1.52 sensor size and 12000x9000 pixels. The sensor will use pixel binning technology to give 12MP photos and 108MP on demand photos. The sensor along with the processor also supports 4K UHD 120fps videos with 3x in-sensor zoom. 
The phone is expected to officially launch on March 24,2021. It will be powered by the SD720G. There will be a 4,500mAh battery with 65W wired charging.
The expected price is around Rs.25000
